The paper deals with the problem of successive refinement, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The paper also involves source coding and decoding, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). The use of side information (SI) is another important aspect of the paper, which is a topic in signal processing and information theory (cs.SI). The paper also involves communication between the encoder and decoders, which is a topic in distributed systems (cs.DS).
